383
00:23:04,661 --> 00:23:05,777
Let's go in.

384
00:23:05,777 --> 00:23:07,837
No, wait. A-Are we going inside?

385
00:23:07,837 --> 00:23:09,212
- Of course.
- I'm leaving.

386
00:23:09,212 --> 00:23:11,861
Don't ditch me, you traitor.

387
00:23:11,861 --> 00:23:16,628
It's physically impossible to meet him, while tailing him.

388
00:23:19,877 --> 00:23:21,754
