389
00:23:21,754 --> 00:23:23,477
You're right.

390
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:28,454
Let me see... champagne, please.

391
00:23:28,454 --> 00:23:30,187
Champagne? Certainly, Sir.

392
00:23:30,187 --> 00:23:32,220
That's all for now.

393
00:23:47,003 --> 00:23:49,112
Haruka's late.

394
00:23:49,112 --> 00:23:51,087
Yes, she is.

395
00:23:56,837 --> 00:23:58,796
