[Hello!]

397
00:24:03,453 --> 00:24:05,170
[Musashi is sad.]

398
00:24:07,087 --> 00:24:08,712
Is that work-related?

399
00:24:09,579 --> 00:24:11,970
No, it's not.

400
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:17,554
I'm going to the bathroom.

401
00:24:33,737 --> 00:24:37,877
