404
00:24:45,930 --> 00:24:48,780
[Toilet]

405
00:24:51,877 --> 00:24:55,062
I thought I'd give you my progress report.

406
00:24:55,712 --> 00:24:57,877
Progress report?

407
00:24:57,877 --> 00:25:03,012
I want to come clean with my wife,

408
00:25:03,012 --> 00:25:06,477
but I couldn't find the right time.

409
00:25:07,161 --> 00:25:09,477
So currently, it's still pending.

410
00:25:15,337 --> 00:25:17,496
I understand.

411
00:25:19,504 --> 00:25:21,154
Haru-tan.

412
00:25:22,261 --> 00:25:25,062
I've missed you so much...

413
00:25:26,654 --> 00:25:28,517
that it made me tremble.

414
00:25:29,654 --> 00:25:31,677
Director, not here.

415
00:25:31,677 --> 00:25:36,937
I know we should wait, but dinner wouldn't hurt.

416
00:25:36,937 --> 00:25:38,687
Can we?

417
00:25:40,212 --> 00:25:41,612
Sure.

418
00:25:56,629 --> 00:25:58,877
How did he spot you?

419
00:25:58,877 --> 00:26:01,537
I'm so sorry, Ma'am.

420
00:26:02,378 --> 00:26:06,462
Come back here now. Haruka is coming.

421
00:26:06,462 --> 00:26:08,877
Look, regarding that...

422
00:26:08,877 --> 00:26:10,478
What?

423
00:26:11,754 --> 00:26:13,295
Haru-tan.

424
00:26:13,295 --> 00:26:16,577
Did he just say Haruka?

425
00:26:16,577 --> 00:26:18,337
No, he didn't.

426
00:26:18,337 --> 00:26:19,961
Haru-tan.

427
00:26:19,961 --> 00:26:23,080
What's he saying?

428
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:24,912
Haru-tan.

429
00:26:26,087 --> 00:26:27,687
Yes?

430
00:26:28,378 --> 00:26:32,410
May I go to the bathroom?

431
00:26:32,410 --> 00:26:34,860
- Haru-tan.
- Of course.

432
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:57,290
[Toilet]

433
00:26:57,295 --> 00:26:58,670
What on earth were you doing?

434
00:26:58,670 --> 00:26:59,587
I'm sorry.

435
00:26:59,587 --> 00:27:00,670
She'll be here soon.

436
00:27:00,670 --> 00:27:03,877
No, she won't. She cancelled last minute.

437
00:27:03,877 --> 00:27:06,001
- We'd better go.
- Why should we?

438
00:27:06,001 --> 00:27:08,270
Let's leave before he spots us.

439
00:28:21,877 --> 00:28:25,512
I have urgent matters to attend, so I have to leave.

440
00:28:25,512 --> 00:28:27,312
I'm sorry.

441
00:28:32,990 --> 00:28:36,290
Ugh, seriously.

442
00:28:36,295 --> 00:28:40,645
I'm so exhausted. What should I do?

443
00:28:42,504 --> 00:28:44,087
What's wrong?

444
00:28:44,087 --> 00:28:46,003
Why did you meddle in my business?

445
00:28:46,003 --> 00:28:47,337
"Meddle in your business"?

446
00:28:47,337 --> 00:28:48,712
Why are you so pissed off?

447
00:28:48,712 --> 00:28:52,877
You told Takekawa that I'm somewhat troubled.

448
00:28:52,877 --> 00:28:56,378
Oh, that? Well...

449
00:28:56,378 --> 00:28:59,337
I thought he was being harsh on you lately.

450
00:28:59,337 --> 00:29:01,087
- So?
- So...

451
00:29:01,087 --> 00:29:05,877
I'm your senior, so I wondered if there's anything I can help you with.

452
00:29:05,877 --> 00:29:11,103
If that's the case, why did you ask Takekawa and not me?

453
00:29:13,004 --> 00:29:14,977
You're hopelessly insensitive.

454
00:29:14,977 --> 00:29:19,404
He is a bit of a perfectionist, so don't take it to heart.

455
00:29:19,404 --> 00:29:21,570
