459
00:29:40,977 --> 00:29:42,745
Welcome.

460
00:29:42,745 --> 00:29:44,877
How come you're here?

461
00:29:44,877 --> 00:29:47,970
Is this your favorite bar, too?

462
00:29:47,970 --> 00:29:49,529
