463
00:29:49,529 --> 00:29:53,404
Don't invade my territory.

464
00:29:53,404 --> 00:29:55,295
Sorry.

465
00:29:55,295 --> 00:29:58,837
I missed Chi-chan so much that I trembled.

466
00:29:58,837 --> 00:30:00,253
Don't tremble over me.

467
00:30:00,253 --> 00:30:03,477
Nice. I love that attitude in a woman.

468
00:30:03,477 --> 00:30:04,909
Go on a date with me.

469
00:30:04,909 --> 00:30:06,696
Let me think about it.

470
00:30:06,696 --> 00:30:08,629
Come on. Why not?

471
00:30:08,629 --> 00:30:10,629
Okay, I'm out of here.

472
00:30:10,629 --> 00:30:13,828
Wait. Try my new dish.

473
00:30:13,828 --> 00:30:15,970
- Next time.
- I insist.

474
00:30:15,970 --> 00:30:18,209
- Next time.
- Wait.

475
00:30:20,087 --> 00:30:22,370
What's with that face?

476
00:30:22,370 --> 00:30:23,993
Is this play time?

477
00:30:23,993 --> 00:30:27,177
Stop messing around. You're coming in, after all.

478
00:30:37,360 --> 00:30:39,262
No perfume.

479
00:30:41,290 --> 00:30:43,496
Receipts will tell me.

480
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:52,161
Oh, that's me. Wrong way.

481
00:30:56,170 --> 00:30:57,770
