525
00:34:03,420 --> 00:34:06,854
- Give us a minute, please.
- Sure.

526
00:34:11,430 --> 00:34:14,003
Somewhere deep inside me,

527
00:34:14,610 --> 00:34:17,950
I still trusted him.

528
00:34:17,950 --> 00:34:19,120
Choko!

529
00:34:19,120 --> 00:34:20,680
