Yes, but...

538
00:35:00,540 --> 00:35:02,145
What is it?

539
00:35:04,870 --> 00:35:09,961
I think it's wrong to walk out without a fight.

540
00:35:09,961 --> 00:35:14,345
I still have some pride left, you know?

541
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:20,612
I don't want to cling to him when some woman has won over his heart.

542
00:35:20,612 --> 00:35:22,529
I understand that. I really do.

543
00:35:22,529 --> 00:35:28,437
But I still think you should tell him your true feelings.

544
00:35:28,437 --> 00:35:33,937
You're a couple that has been together for 30 years.

545
00:35:40,270 --> 00:35:41,980
The Director is...

546
00:35:41,980 --> 00:35:47,100
not a coward who runs away from reality.

547
00:35:53,290 --> 00:35:55,554
You...

548
00:35:55,554 --> 00:36:00,562
You really are... kind-hearted.

549
00:36:03,610 --> 00:36:05,937
You're wrong.

550
00:36:06,650 --> 00:36:08,503
I...

551
00:36:09,770 --> 00:36:14,470
I'm not kind-hearted or a good man.

552
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:22,295
Why are you crying?

553
00:36:22,295 --> 00:36:26,310
[Azeriya]

554
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:33,620
[Azeriya]

555
00:36:39,530 --> 00:36:41,170
Choko.

556
00:36:42,103 --> 00:36:43,970
Choko!

557
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,987
Director?

558
00:36:47,987 --> 00:36:51,820
Why is he here, Choko?

559
00:36:51,820 --> 00:36:54,861
He was giving me advices on my new apartment.

560
00:36:54,861 --> 00:36:57,850
So late at night?

561
00:36:57,850 --> 00:36:59,820
You're crying.

562
00:36:59,820 --> 00:37:02,561
- Did you upset her?
- No, not me.

563
00:37:02,561 --> 00:37:05,304
There's something I must tell you.

564
00:37:06,180 --> 00:37:07,887
Me, too.

565
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:12,578
All right then. I'll get going.

566
00:37:12,578 --> 00:37:15,288
- Don't go.
- No, you stay.

567
00:37:21,970 --> 00:37:25,270
I need to know the reason of our divorce.

568
00:37:25,270 --> 00:37:27,003
Have you grown to hate me?

569
00:37:27,003 --> 00:37:29,312
That's not it.

570
00:37:29,312 --> 00:37:31,770
You're still very precious to me.

571
00:37:31,770 --> 00:37:36,077
That hasn't changed in 30 years. But...

572
00:37:39,570 --> 00:37:42,487
I'm in love with someone else now.

573
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:45,377
I'm sorry.

574
00:37:48,370 --> 00:37:51,204
You love Haru-tan, right?

575
00:37:54,330 --> 00:37:56,645
Who is she?

576
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:04,777
Let me grab a salad...

577
00:38:04,777 --> 00:38:07,828
- from the salad bar.
- No, stay put.

578
00:38:07,828 --> 00:38:09,378
Stay put.

579
00:38:09,378 --> 00:38:13,729
Listen, can't you break up with Haruka?

580
00:38:14,340 --> 00:38:16,920
It's not Haruka, but Haru-tan.

581
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:18,504
Who cares about that?

582
00:38:18,504 --> 00:38:21,020
Let's stop here, Director and Mrs. Kurosawa.

583
00:38:21,020 --> 00:38:23,395
What kind of woman is she?

584
00:38:24,570 --> 00:38:26,603
It's not a woman.

585
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:36,629
Haru-tan isn't a woman.

586
00:38:38,540 --> 00:38:40,120
What?

587
00:38:41,610 --> 00:38:43,677
Haru-tan is...

588
00:38:45,870 --> 00:38:47,777
a man.

589
00:38:53,190 --> 00:38:54,760
Wait...

590
00:38:56,040 --> 00:38:57,877
I don't understand.

591
00:38:57,877 --> 00:39:02,162
I didn't have the courage to tell you this.

592
00:39:02,162 --> 00:39:04,353
I'm sorry.

593
00:39:04,353 --> 00:39:08,720
What? You love a man?

594
00:39:08,720 --> 00:39:12,020
You're very precious to me,

595
00:39:12,020 --> 00:39:18,220
that's why I want you to know the real me.

596
00:39:19,550 --> 00:39:22,837
The person I'm in love with is...

597
00:39:38,180 --> 00:39:40,053
him.

598
00:39:43,330 --> 00:39:45,037
No way!

599
00:39:47,330 --> 00:39:49,477
What's your name?

600
00:39:51,750 --> 00:39:54,328
I'm Haru-tan.

601
00:40:02,337 --> 00:40:04,550
[Ossan's Love]
